10. state.rs: global state accumulation

This file defines the lived-in world of guilds, rooms, members, and submissions.

Main types

Principal
Contains:
	•	pubkey
	•	roles
	•	reputation
	•	bond balance

So membership is not merely identity; it carries governance and economic metadata.

RoomState
Contains:
	•	room ID
	•	members map
	•	submission list

GuildState
Contains:
	•	guild ID
	•	optional constitution
	•	rooms map

